com.inchok.aria2

Class Gid

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inchok.aria2.Gid

  • public class Gid
extends java.lang.Object
    The unique identifier of each download.

    In fact, gid is a 64-bits number.

    To create a custom gid, use static method Gid.toGid(String).

    Version:
    Version 1.0
    Author:
    inCHOK
